WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.509 --> 00:00:07.509
Mobil kecil, berwarna jingga, beroda tiga,
satu pengemudi.

00:00:07.509 --> 00:00:08.509
Stop, bajaj, stop!

00:00:08.509 --> 00:00:09.509
Tolong, Pak, kami diantar.

00:00:09.509 --> 00:00:21.270
Lalu bajaj pun berputar.

00:00:21.270 --> 00:00:26.039
Zuiiiing!

00:00:26.039 --> 00:00:27.039
Kami bersandar.

00:00:27.039 --> 00:00:28.360
Tangan Ibu melingkar.

00:00:28.360 --> 00:00:45.499
Angin semilir menghembus rambut Ali.

00:00:45.499 --> 00:01:10.650
Ketika bajaj pergi menderu, melintasi laju
lalu lintas.

00:01:10.650 --> 00:01:16.340
Bergetar dan bergetar.

00:01:16.340 --> 00:01:25.600
Lembut bergetar, seperti adik bayi dalam buaian.

00:01:25.600 --> 00:01:27.640
Bergetar dan bergetar.

00:01:27.640 --> 00:01:34.910
Angin berhembus membawa Ali menembus mimpi
yang indah.

00:01:34.910 --> 00:01:35.910
Hoaaahhm.

00:01:35.910 --> 00:01:36.910
"Bangun, Ali!

00:01:36.910 --> 00:01:37.910
Bangunlah!

00:01:37.910 --> 00:01:38.910
Kita sudah sampai!"

00:01:38.910 --> 00:01:39.910
Suara Ibu lembut terdengar.

00:01:39.910 --> 00:01:41.820
Sampai jumpa, bajaj!

00:01:41.820 --> 00:01:46.450
Terimakasih telah mengantarku pulang.

00:01:46.450 --> 00:02:02.140
Besok antar Ali lagi, ya!

00:02:02.140 --> 00:02:20.809
Ali suka naik bajaj!

